cast.overview: A tormented jazz musician finds himself lost in an enigmatic story involving murder, surveillance, gangsters, doppelgängers, and an impossible transformation inside a prison cell.
cast.title: Lost Highway

details.biography:
From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.

Jennifer Maria Syme (December 7, 1972 – April 2, 2001) was an American actress and production assistant. She was best known for her role in Lost Highway, and for her relationship with actor Keanu Reeves.
